# Sanidhya

Personal portfolio built with a focus on clean aesthetics, thoughtful interactions, and modern web engineering.

---

## Overview

A full-stack portfolio designed to combine minimal design with dynamic functionality.  
The project reflects my journey through development, competitive programming, and systems thinking.

---

## Stack

### Frontend
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

### APIs & Integrations
- Codeforces API
- GitHub API
- Chart.js

---

## Features

- Responsive cinematic interface
- Real-time Codeforces rating graph
- Dynamic GitHub profile integration
- Smooth transitions and animations
- Interactive coding profile section
- Structured and scalable architecture

---

## Structure

```txt
Portfolio-Website/

├── Client/
│   ├── assets/
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── style.css
│   └── script.js
│
├── Server/
│   └── server.js
│
├── package-lock.json
├── package.json
└── README.md
```

---

## Local Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/SanidhyaDigvijay/sanidhya-portfolio-website
```

```bash
npm install
```

```bash
node Server/server.js
```

Open `Client/index.html` using Live Server.

---

## Deployment

Frontend deployed on Vercel.  
Backend deployed on Render.

---

## Live

https://sanidhya-portfolio-website.vercel.app


